The paper discusses the security threats and vulnerabilities associated with the networking of drones, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also mentions the use of cellular networks for IoD, which relates to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the challenges and research directions for securing IoD, which falls under the categories of systems and control (cs.SY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
